title: The cloud changes IT culture, demands new tech skills
text:
15 The cloud changes IT culture, demands new tech skills 
Computerworld: As enterprises are moving to the cloud, it's changing a whole lot more than just where companies' data and services are sitting.The emergence of the cloud is heralding a shift in the skills that IT workers need and the jobs they are doing. It's changing the entire culture inside IT departments.
